item.title: CVE-2017-16169|2024-09-16T16:33:44.847Z -- hackerone -- looppake%20node%20module
item.description: looppake is a simple http server. looppake is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
